T* (Abstract) Tj
T* (Anomaly detectors often output uncalibrated scores that are hard to threshold operationally.) Tj
T* (We combine isotonic calibration with conformal prediction and show reliable coverage on five) Tj
T* (tabular datasets without retraining the base model.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Keywords: anomaly detection, calibration, conformal prediction, tabular data) Tj
T* () Tj
